your needs. STARS AND SCORING
Registration
Upon registering for MM, you will be asked to self-certify your ability based on a 5-star rating (5 being the best and 1 being beginner level)
Adjustments
MM will make adjustments to this rating based on your previous 5 results in the interest of trying to keep matches as fair as possible.
Head starts
To make all matches as even as possible, the following head starts will be given for every 5 frames played:
5-star Vs 1 or 2 star = 2 head start
5-star Vs 3 star = 1 head start
4-star Vs 1 or 2 star = 1 head start
So, if 5-star plays 2-star for 15 frames, 6 frame lead will be registered.
Scoring
MM provides an in-app scorecard to allow you to track the score of your match.
Upon completion of match, your match score will be recorded by MM and posted on your history
Each score will contribute towards adjusting the star rating.
